y'=>'每月','Fortnightly'=>'每 2 週','Weekly'=>'每週','Daily'=>'每日','12 Hours'=>'每 12 小時','Overwrite existing pages'=>'覆寫現有頁面','Import Setting'=>'匯入設定','- Select -'=>'- 選取 -','Select an existing author:'=>'選取現有的作者:','Assign author'=>'指派作者','The importing file info'=>'匯入檔案資訊','Scan Uploaded Exports'=>'掃描已上載的匯出檔案','Upload and Import'=>'上載並匯入','Choose an export from your computer to import: '=>'從使用者個人裝置選取匯出檔案以進行匯入: ','Delete Exported Files In Folder'=>'刪除資料夾中的匯出檔案','To properly display the imported content, please make sure that the importing and exporting sites have the same environment, for example, same theme or pages built with the same page builder.'=>'想要正確顯示匯入的內容，請確定要匯入內容的網站與匯出內容的網站有相同的環境；舉例來說，使用相同的佈景主題或頁面編輯器。','Import posts or pages with images in bulk.'=>'批次匯入文章或頁面 (包含內容中的圖片)。','File not found. Please retry again.'=>'找不到條件相符的檔案，請再試一次。','File size not match. please retry again.'=>'檔案大小不相符，請再試一次。','Task time out.'=>'工作已逾時。','Export error:'=>'匯出時發生錯誤:','The export task is not responding.'=>'匯出工作沒有回應。','Ready to export. Progress: 0%, running time: 0second.'=>'匯出工作準備就緒。進度: 0%，執行時間: 0 秒。','Error occurred while parsing the request data. Please try to run export task again.'=>'剖析要求的資料時發生錯誤，請嘗試再次執行匯出工作。','Empty post id'=>'空白文章 ID','Export and Download'=>'匯出並下載','Sample:'=>'範例:','Only letters (except for wpvivid) and numbers are allowed.'=>'只能使用英文字母及數字撰寫註解，但不能使用 wpvivid 這個字。','Comment the export: '=>'撰寫匯出檔案註解: ','Comment the export (optional)'=>'撰寫匯出檔案註解 (選用)','&mdash; Select &mdash;'=>'&mdash; 選取 &mdash;','All Authors'=>'全部作者','All Categories'=>'全部分類','Filter Posts/Pages'=>'篩選文章/頁面','Choose what to export'=>'選取匯出項目','Next Step'=>'下一步','More post types coming soon...'=>'即將支援更多內容類型...','Page'=>'頁面','Post'=>'文章','Choose post type'=>'選取內容類型','Try to select fewer items when you are facing a shortage of server resources (typically presented as a timeout error).'=>'伺服器發生資源不足的狀況時 (通常為逾時錯誤)，請嘗試選取較少的項目。','Note:'=>'注意事項:','This will contain all of your posts, pages, comments, terms and images (original images, featured images and thumbnails).'=>'這項操作會納入這個網站的全部文章、頁面、留言、分類法詞彙及圖片 (原始圖片、精選圖片及縮圖)。','Learn more'=>'進一步了解','Export posts or pages with images in bulk.'=>'批次匯出文章或頁面 (包含內容中的圖片)。','Export & Import'=>'匯出及匯入','Last Modified'=>'最後修改日期','Scheduled'=>'已排程','Missed schedule'=>'已錯過排程','Published'=>'已發佈','Unpublished'=>'已取消發佈','Comments'=>'留言','Author'=>'作者','column nameTitle'=>'標題','Note: The files you want to upload must be a backup created by WPvivid backup plugin. Make sure that uploading every part of a backup to the directory if the backup is split into many parts'=>'注意事項: 要上載的檔案必須由 WPvivid Backup 外掛建立。如果備份檔案已分割為多個部分，則必須將全部分割檔案上載至目前外掛指定的目錄。','Upload'=>'上載','Transfer succeeded. Please scan the backup list on the destination site to display the backup, then restore the backup.'=>'傳輸已完成。請掃描目標網站的備份檔案清單以顯示備份檔案，然後使用備份檔案進行還原。','Choose what to migrate'=>'自行選取要移轉的項目','3. Once done, the backup appears in backups list. Then, restore the backup.'=>'3. 以上操作完成後，備份檔案便會出現目標網站的備份檔案清單中，點擊對應的 [還原] 按鈕即可透過備份檔案還原網站。','2.1 Upload the backup to the upload section of WPvivid backup plugin in destination site.'=>'2.1 在目標網站的 WPvivid Backup 外掛的 [備份及還原]&rarr;[上載] 區段中上載備份檔案。','2. Upload the backup to destination site. There are two ways available to use:'=>'2. 將備份檔案上載至目標網站。以下提供 2 種可用的方式:','1. Download a backup in backups list to your computer.'=>'1. 在備份檔案清單中依據需求下載需要的備份檔案至使用者個人裝置。','How to migrate Wordpress site manually to a new domain(site) with WPvivid backup plugin?'=>'使用 WPvivid Backup 外掛手動移轉 WordPress 網站至新網域名稱 (網站) 的方式','2. Please migrate website with the manual way when using <strong>Local by Flywheel</strong> environment.'=>'2. 如果這個網站使用 <strong>Local by Flywheel</strong> 環境建置，請改以手動方式移轉網站。','1. In order to successfully complete the migration, you\'d better deactivate <a href="https://wpvivid.com/best-redirect-plugins.html" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;">301 redirect plugin</a>, <a href="https://wpvivid.com/8-best-wordpress-firewall-plugins.html" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;">firewall and security plugin</a>, and <a href="https://wpvivid.com/best-free-wordpress-caching-plugins.html" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;">caching plugin</a> (if they exist) before transferring website.'=>'1. 為了成功完成移轉，如果這個網站上使用 <a href="https://wpvivid.com/best-redirect-plugins.html" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;">301 重新導向</a>、<a href="https://wpvivid.com/8-best-wordpress-firewall-plugins.html" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;">防火牆/安全性</a>及<a href="https://wpvivid.com/best-free-wordpress-caching-plugins.html" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;">快取</a>等外掛，建議先停用這些外掛。','Note: '=>'注意事項: ','Choose the content you want to transfer'=>'選取要傳輸的內容','The feature can help you transfer a Wordpress site to a new domain(site). It would be a convenient way to migrate your WP site from dev environment to live server or from old server to the new.'=>'這個功能可以協助網站管理員將 WordPress 網站傳輸至新的網域名稱 (網站)。無論是要將 WordPress 網站從開發環境移轉至正式伺服器，或是要將 WordPress 網站從舊伺服器移轉至新伺服器，都是非常方便的方式。','3. Go back to this page and paste the key in key box below. Lastly, click Save button.'=>'3. 返回這個頁面，並在下方金鑰欄位貼上金鑰內容，然後請點擊 [儲存] 按鈕。','2. Generate a key by clicking Generate button and copy it.'=>'2. 點擊 [產生] 按鈕以產生金鑰，並複製金鑰內容。','1. Visit Key tab page of WPvivid backup plugin of destination site.'=>'1. 前往目標網站的 WPvivid Backup 外掛的 [金鑰] 分頁。','How to get a site key?'=>'取得網站金鑰的方式','Please paste the key below.'=>'請在下方欄位貼上金鑰。','A task is already running. Please wait until the running task is complete, and try again.'=>'工作正在執行。請稍做等待至這項工作完成，然後再試一次。','Generate'=>'產生','Tips: For security reason, please choose an appropriate expiration time for the key.'=>'使用提示: 基於安全性考量，請為金鑰選取合適的到期時間。','The key will expire in '=>'金鑰到期時間: ','In order to allow another site to send a backup to this site, please generate a key below. Once the key is generated, this site is ready to receive a backup from another site. Then, please copy and paste the key in sending site and save it.'=>'如需開放其他網站傳送備份檔案至這個網站，請在下方產生金鑰。金鑰產生後，這個網站便能接收來自其他網站的備份檔案。請複製金鑰，然後在要傳送備份檔案的網站中貼上並儲存。','Key'=>'金鑰','Auto-Migration'=>'自動移轉','Unable to send email. Please check the configuration of email server.'=>'無法傳送電子郵件。請檢查電子郵件伺服器組態。','Unable to create directory %s. Is its parent directory writable by the server?'=>'無法建立目錄 %s。它的上層目錄是否可由伺服器進行寫入？','The log not found.'=>'找不到符合條件的記錄。','Reading the log failed. Please try again.'=>'無法讀取記錄。請再試一次。','Unable to open the log file.'=>'無法開啟記錄檔。','Error occurred while parsing the request data. Please try to run backup again.'=>'剖析要求的資料時發生錯誤，請嘗試再次執行備份程序。','Click the button to connect to SFTP server and add it to the storage list below.'=>'點擊按鈕以連線至 SFTP 伺服器，並將它新增至下方儲存空間清單。','Enter an absolute path and a custom subdirectory (optional) for holding the backups of current website. For example, /var/customfolder/'=>'輸入用於儲存這個網站備份檔案的絕對路徑及自訂子目錄 (後者為選填)，例如 /var/customfolder/。','Absolute path must exist(e.g. /var)'=>'絕對路徑必須存在 (例如 /var)','Enter the server port.'=>'輸入伺服器通訊埠號碼。','Port'=>'通訊埠','Enter the user password.'=>'輸入使用者密碼。','User Password'=>'使用者密碼','Enter the user name.'=>'輸入使用者名稱。','User Name'=>'使用者名稱','Enter the server address.'=>'輸入伺服器位址。','Server Address'=>'伺服器位址','Enter a unique alias: e.g. SFTP-001'=>'輸入唯一別名 (例如 SFTP-001)','SFTP'=>'SFTP','The simplexml extension is not detected. Please install the extension first.'=>'系統沒有偵測到 simplexml 擴充功能。請先安裝這個擴充功能。','Click the button to connect to Amazon S3 storage and add it to the storage list below.'=>'點擊按鈕以連線至 Amazon S3 儲存空間，並將它新增至下方儲存空間清單。','Check the option to use Amazon S3 server-side encryption to protect data.'=>'啟用這項設定後，便能使用 Amazon S3 伺服器端加密保護資料。','Server-side encryption.'=>'伺服器端加密','Check the option to use Amazon S3 Standard-Infrequent Access (S3 Standard-IA) storage class for data transfer.'=>'啟用這項設定後，便能在資料傳輸時使用 Amazon S3 Standard-Infrequent Access (S3 Standard-IA) 儲存類別。','Storage class: Standard (infrequent access).'=>'儲存類別: 標準 (不常存取方案)','Customize the directory where you want to store backups within the Bucket.'=>'自訂儲存貯體用於儲存備份檔案的目錄。','Enter an existed Bucket to create a custom backup storage directory.'=>'輸入現有的儲存貯體以建立自訂備份檔案儲存空間目錄。','Amazon S3 Bucket Name(e.g. test)'=>'Amazon S3 儲存貯體名稱 (例如 test)','How to get an Amazon S3 secret key.'=>'取得 Amazon S3 秘密金鑰的方式','Enter your Amazon S3 secret key.'=>'輸入 Amazon S3 秘密金鑰。','Amazon S3 secret key'=>'Amazon S3 秘密金鑰','How to get an AmazonS3 access key.'=>'取得 Amazon S3 存取金鑰的方式','Enter your Amazon S3 access key.'=>'輸入 Amazon S3 存取金鑰。','Amazon S3 access key'=>'Amazon S3 存取金鑰','Enter a unique alias: e.g. Amazon S3-001'=>'輸入唯一別名 (例如 Amazon S3-001)','Amazon S3'=>'Amazon S3','Authenticate with Microsoft OneDrive'=>'取得 Microsoft OneDrive 驗證','Enter a unique alias: e.g. OneDrive-001'=>'輸入唯一別名 (例如 OneDrive-001)','Enter Your Microsoft OneDrive Information'=>'輸入 Microsoft OneDrive 資訊','Microsoft OneDrive'=>'Microsoft OneDrive','Authenticate with Google Drive'=>'取得 Google 雲端硬碟驗證','Enter a unique alias: e.g. Google Drive-001'=>'輸入唯一別名 (例如 Google Drive-001)','Enter Your Google Drive Information'=>'輸入 Google 雲端硬碟資訊','Google Drive'=>'Google 雲端硬碟','Authentication failed, the format of the client_secrets.json file is incorrect. Please delete and re-install the plugin to recreate the file.'=>'驗證失敗，client_secrets.json 檔案格式不正確。請刪除並重新安裝外掛以重新建立這個檔案。','Authentication failed, the client_secrets.json file is missing. Please make sure the client_secrets.json file is in wpvivid-backuprestore\\includes\\customclass directory.'=>'驗證失敗，找不到 client_secrets.json 檔案。請確定 client_secrets.json 檔案存在於 wpvivid-backuprestore\\includes\\customclass 目錄。','Click the button to connect to DigitalOcean Spaces storage and add it to the storage list below.'=>'點擊按鈕以連線至 DigitalOcean Spaces 儲存空間，並將它新增至下方儲存空間清單。','Enter the DigitalOcean Endpoint for the storage'=>'輸入 DigitalOcean 儲存空間的端點。','region.digitaloceanspaces.com'=>'例如 region.digitaloceanspaces.com','Customize the directory where you want to store backups within the Space.'=>'自訂 Space 用於儲存備份檔案的目錄。','Custom Path'=>'自訂路徑','Enter an existed Space to create a custom backup storage directory.'=>'輸入現有的 Space 以建立自訂備份檔案儲存空間目錄。','Space Name(e.g. test)'=>'Space 名稱 (例如 test)','Enter your DigitalOcean Spaces secret key'=>'輸入 DigitalOcean Spaces 祕密金鑰。','DigitalOcean Spaces secret key'=>'DigitalOcean Spaces 祕密金鑰','Enter your DigitalOcean Spaces access key'=>'輸入 DigitalOcean Spaces 存取金鑰。','DigitalOcean Spaces access key'=>'DigitalOcean Spaces 存取金鑰','Enter a unique alias: e.g. DOS-001'=>'輸入唯一別名 (例如 DOS-001)','DigitalOcean Spaces'=>'DigitalOcean Spaces','Click the button to connect to FTP server and add it to the storage list below.'=>'點擊按鈕以連線至 FTP 伺服器，並將它新增至下方儲存空間清單。','Test and Add'=>'測試並新增','Uncheck the option to use FTP active mode when transferring files. Make sure the FTP server you are configuring supports the active FTP mode.'=>'停用這項設定後，便能在傳輸檔案時使用 FTP 主動模式。請確定 FTP 伺服器已組態為支援 FTP 主動模式。','Uncheck this to enable FTP active mode.'=>'停用這項設定便能使用 FTP 主動模式','Enter an absolute path and a custom subdirectory (optional) for holding the backups of current website. For example, /home/username/customfolder'=>'輸入用於儲存這個網站備份檔案的絕對路徑及自訂子目錄 (後者為選填)，例如 /home/username/customfolder。','Absolute path must exist(e.g. /home/username)'=>'絕對路徑必須存在 (例如 /home/username)','Enter the FTP server password.'=>'輸入 FTP 伺服器密碼。','FTP password'=>'FTP 密碼','Enter your FTP server user name.'=>'輸入 FTP 伺服器使用者名稱。','FTP login'=>'FTP 使用者名稱','Pro feature: Change the FTP default port number'=>'Pro 版功能: 變更 FTP 預設通訊埠號碼','Enter the FTP server.'=>'輸入 FTP 伺服器','FTP server (server\'s port 21)'=>'FTP 伺服器 (伺服器通訊埠號碼 21)','Enter an unique alias: e.g. FTP-001'=>'輸入唯一別名 (例如 FTP-001)','FTP'=>'FTP','Click the button to save the changes.'=>'點擊按鈕以儲存變更。','Authenticate with Dropbox'=>'取得 Dropbox 驗證','Once checked, all this sites backups sent to a remote storage destination will be uploaded to this storage by default.'=>'啟用這項設定後，這個網站要傳送至遠端儲存空間的全部備份檔案，預設都會上載至這個遠端儲存空間。','Set as the default remote storage.'=>'設定為預設遠端儲存空間','Pro feature: Create a directory for storing the backups of the site'=>'Pro 版功能: 建立用於儲存網站備份檔案的目錄','All backups will be uploaded to this directory.'=>'全部備份檔案會上載至這個目錄。','Enter a unique alias: e.g. Dropbox-001'=>'輸入唯一別名 (例如 Dropbox-001)','Enter Your Dropbox Information'=>'輸入 Dropbox 資訊','Dropbox'=>'Dropbox','The backup will be canceled after backing up the current chunk ends.'=>'備份程序會在完成備份目前的區塊後取消。','A name to help you identify the storage if you have multiple remote storage connected.'=>'如果連線至多個遠端儲存空間，有意義的名稱可以協助網站管理員識別儲存空間。','running time: '=>'執行時間: ','Progress: '=>'進度: ','Ready to backup. Progress: 0%, running time: 0second.'=>'備份工作準備就緒。進度: 0%，執行時間: 0 秒。','This does not appear to be a WXR file, missing/invalid WXR version number'=>'由於找不到版本號碼或版本號碼無效，系統判定這不是 WXR 格式的檔案。','Details are shown above. The importer will now try again with a different parser...'=>'詳細資訊如上所示。匯入程式將以不同的剖析器再次嘗試匯入...','There was an error when reading this WXR file'=>'讀取 WXR 檔案時發生錯誤','Invalid file type'=>'無效的檔案類型','Fetching attachments is not enabled'=>'[擷取附件] 未啟用','Sorry, this file type is not permitted for security reasons.'=>'很抱歉，基於安全性考量，系統不接受這個檔案類型。','Last page'=>'最後一頁','Next page'=>'下一頁','paging%1$s of %2$s'=>'第 %1$s 頁，總計 %2$s 頁','Previous page'=>'上一頁','First page'=>'第一頁','Current Page'=>'目前頁數','%s item'=>'%s 個項目','Type: '=>'類型: ','Media Files Size'=>'媒體檔案大小','Count'=>'項目數量','Post Types'=>'內容類型','File Name'=>'檔案名稱','Select Files'=>'選取檔案','Uploader: Drop files here - or - Select Filesor'=>'或','Drop files here'=>'請將檔案拖放至這裡上載','Scan uploaded backup or received backup'=>'掃描已上載備份或已接收備份','Tips: Click the button below to scan all uploaded or received backups in directory'=>'使用提示: 點擊下方按鈕以掃描目錄中全部已上載或已接收的備份。目錄:','Warning: There is no default remote storage available for the scheduled backups, please set up it first.'=>'警告: 沒有可供排程備份使用的預設遠端儲存空間，請先進行這項設定。','Next Backup: '=>'下次備份時間: ','Server Time: '=>'伺服器時間: ','Schedule Status: '=>'排程狀態: ','Backup Schedule'=>'備份排程','The settings are only for manual backup, which won\'t affect schedule settings.'=>'這些設定僅會套用至手動備份，不會影響排程設定。','This backup can only be deleted manually'=>'這個備份檔案僅能手動刪除','Backup Now'=>'立即備份','Send Backup to Remote Storage:'=>'傳送備份檔案至遠端儲存空間:','Save Backups to Local'=>'儲存備份檔案至網站主機','rename directory'=>'重新命名目錄','Local Storage Directory:'=>'網站主機本機儲存目錄:','Back Up Manually'=>'手動備份','Cancel'=>'取消','Network Connection:'=>'網路連線:','Speed:'=>'速度:','Uploaded:'=>'已上載:','The backup is stored on the remote storage, click on the button to download it to localhost.'=>'備份檔案以儲存於遠端儲存空間，點擊按鈕便能將備份檔案下載至網站主機本機。','Retrieve the backup to localhost'=>'將備份檔案擷取至網站主機本機','Restore function will replace the current site\'s themes, plugins, uploads, database and/or other content directories with the existing equivalents in the selected backup.'=>'還原功能會以選取的備份檔案中的佈景主題、外掛、上載的檔案、資料庫及其他內容目錄的項目，取代將這個網站目前的對應項目。','Please do not close the page or switch to other pages when a restore task is running, as it could trigger some unexpected errors.'=>'執行還原工作時，請不要關閉這個頁面切換至其他頁面，這會觸發未預期的錯誤。','Restore backup from:'=>'還原來源備份檔案: ','Step Three: Click \'Restore\' button'=>'步驟 3: 點擊 [還原] 按鈕。','Step Two: Choose an option to complete restore, if any'=>'步驟 2: 選取系統提供可完整還原的選項。','Step One: In the backup list, click the \'Restore\' button on the backup you want to restore. This will bring up the restore tab'=>'步驟 1: 在備份檔案清單中點擊要還原的備份檔案的 [還原] 按鈕，點擊後會開啟 [還原] 分頁。','This request might delete the backup being downloaded, are you sure you want to continue?'=>'這個要求可能會刪除正在下載的備份檔案，確定要繼續操作嗎？','Please select at least one item.'=>'請選取至少一個項目。','This request will delete the backup being downloaded, are you sure you want to continue?'=>'這個要求會刪除正在下載的備份檔案，確定要繼續操作嗎？','This backup is locked, are you sure to remove it? This backup will be deleted permanently from your hosting (localhost) and remote storages.'=>'確定要移除這個已鎖定的備份檔案嗎？這個備份檔案會從這台網站主機 (本機) 及遠端儲存空間永久刪除。','Delete the selected backups'=>'刪除選取的備份檔案','Delete'=>'刪除','Storage'=>'儲存空間','Backup'=>'備份','Restore'=>'還原','Backups'=>'備份','How to restore your website from a backup(scheduled, manual, uploaded and received backup)'=>'從備份檔案還原網站的方式 (排程備份、手動備份、已上載及已接收的備份)','->If backups are stored in web server, the plugin will list all relevant files immediately.'=>'&rarr;備份檔案儲存於網頁伺服器時，這個外掛會立即列出全部相關檔案。','->If backups are stored in remote storage, our plugin will retrieve the backup to your web server first. This may take a little time depending on the size of backup files. Please be patient. Then you can download them to your PC.'=>'&rarr;備份檔案儲存於遠端儲存空間時，這個外掛會先將備份檔案擷取至這個網站的網頁伺服器。','About backup download'=>'進一步了解備份檔案下載','Actions'=>'可用操作','Remote Storage Alias'=>'遠端儲存空間別名','Storage Provider'=>'儲存服務提供商','Please choose one storage to save your backups (remote storage)'=>'請選取儲存空間以儲存這個網站的備份檔案 (遠端儲存空間)','Storage Edit'=>'編輯儲存空間','Storages'=>'儲存空間','Advanced Settings'=>'進階設定','General Settings'=>'一般設定','Chunk Size'=>'區塊大小','Adjust this value to apply for a temporary PHP memory limit for WPvivid backup plugin in restore process. We set this value to 256M by default. Increase the value if you encounter a memory exhausted error. Note: some web hosting providers may not support this.'=>'調整這項設定值便能臨時變更 WPvivid Backup 執行還原程序的 PHP 可存取記憶體上限。這項設定的預設值為 256MB，如果遇到網站耗盡記憶體的錯誤，請增加設定值。請注意，某些網站主機服務提供商不支援這項設定。','PHP Memory Limit for restoration'=>'還原程序的 PHP 可存取記憶體上限','Adjust this value to apply for a temporary PHP memory limit for WPvivid backup plugin to run a backup. We set this value to 256M by default. Increase the value if you encounter a memory exhausted error. Note: some web hosting providers may not support this.'=>'調整這項設定值便能臨時變更 WPvivid Backup 執行備份程序的 PHP 可存取記憶體上限。這項設定的預設值為 256MB，如果遇到網站耗盡記憶體的錯誤，請增加設定值。請注意，某些網站主機服務提供商不支援這項設定。','PHP Memory Limit for backup'=>'備份程序的 PHP 可存取記憶體上限','The time-out is not your server PHP time-out. With the execution time exhausted, our plugin will shut the process of restore down. If the progress of restore encounters a time-out, that means you have a medium or large sized website, please try to scale the value bigger.'=>'這裡所指的逾時不是伺服器上的 PHP 指令碼執行逾時。耗盡執行時間後，這個外掛會關閉還原程序。當還原程序發生執行逾時的狀況，代表這是中型或大型網站，請嘗試加大設定值。','PHP script execution timeout for restore'=>'還原程序的 PHP 指令碼執行逾時時間上限','The time-out is not your server PHP time-out. With the execution time exhausted, our plugin will shut the process of backup down. If the progress of backup encounters a time-out, that means you have a medium or large sized website, please try to scale the value bigger.'=>'這裡所指的逾時不是伺服器上的 PHP 指令碼執行逾時。耗盡執行時間後，這個外掛會關閉備份程序。當備份程序發生執行逾時的狀況，代表這是中型或大型網站，請嘗試加大設定值。','PHP script execution timeout for backup'=>'備份程序的 PHP 指令碼執行逾時時間上限','Using the option will ignore the file larger than the certain size in MB when backing up, \'0\' (zero) means unlimited.'=>'系統會忽略大於這項設定的檔案 (單位為 MB)。設定為 0 代表不限制。','Exclude the files which are larger than'=>'排除大於指定大小的檔案','Compress Files Every'=>'壓縮檔案分割大小','It is recommended to choose PDO option if pdo_mysql extension is installed on your server, which lets you backup and restore your site faster.'=>'如果這台伺服器已安裝 pdo_mysql 擴充功能，建議選取 [PDO] 選項，能讓這個網站的備份及還原更快速。','WPDB option has a better compatibility, but the speed of backup and restore is slower.'=>'[WPDB] 選項有更好的相容性，但是備份及還原的速度較慢。','Database access method.'=>'資料庫存取方式','Importing the json file can help you set WPvivid\'s configuration on another wordpress site quickly.'=>'匯入來自其他 WordPress 網站的 JSON 檔案，可以協助網站管理員快速完成 WPvivid Backup 外掛的組態。','Import'=>'匯入','Click \'Export\' button to save WPvivid settings on your local computer.'=>'點擊 [匯出] 按鈕便能在使用者個人裝置儲存 WPvivid 設定。','Export'=>'匯出','Empty'=>'清空','Calculate Sizes'=>'計算大小','Total Size:'=>'大小總計:','Web-server disk space in use by WPvivid'=>'WPvivid 已使用的網頁伺服器磁碟空間','Pro feature: Add another email address to get report'=>'Pro 版功能: 新增其他電子郵件地址以取得報告','Only send an email notification when a backup fails'=>'僅備份失敗後傳送電子郵件通知','Always send an email notification when a backup is complete'=>'備份完成後一律傳送電子郵件通知','Test Email'=>'測試用電子郵件','Enable email report'=>'啟用電子郵件報告','The action is irreversible! It will remove all backups are out-of-date (including local web server and remote storage) if they exist.'=>'這項操作無法復原，並且會移除網頁伺服器本機及遠端儲存空間上過期的全部備份檔案。','Remove'=>'移除','Remote Storage Directory:'=>'遠端儲存空間目錄:','Web Server Directory:'=>'網頁伺服器目錄:','Remove out-of-date backups'=>'移除過期備份檔案','Display domain(url) of current site in backup name. (e.g. domain_wpvivid-5ceb938b6dca9_2019-05-27-07-36_backup_all.zip)'=>'在備份檔案名稱中顯示目前網站的網域名稱 (網址，例如 domain_wpvivid-5ceb938b6dca9_2019-05-27-07-36_backup_all.zip)','Local storage directory:'=>'網站主機本機儲存目錄:','Name your folder, this folder must be writable for creating backup files.'=>'請命名這個資料夾，外掛必須具備對這個資料夾的寫入權限才能建立備份檔案。','Backup Folder'=>'備份資料夾','Keep storing the backups in localhost after uploading to remote storage'=>'備份檔案上載至遠端儲存空間後，在網站主機本機保留備份檔案','Merge all the backup files into single package when a backup completes. This will save great disk spaces, though takes longer time. We recommended you check the option especially on sites with insufficient server resources.'=>'備份完成時將全部備份檔案合併至單一封裝 (這項設定會節省大量磁碟空間，但會花費較長的處理時間；網站在伺服器資源不足時，特別建議啟用這項設定)','Show WPvivid backup plugin on top admin bar'=>'在頂端管理列顯示 WPvivid Backup 外掛','Calculate the size of files, folder and database before backing up'=>'備份前計算檔案、資料夾及資料庫大小','Pro feature: Retain more backups'=>'Pro 版功能: 保留更多備份檔案','backups retained'=>'份保留備份檔案','Custom'=>'自訂','Only Database'=>'僅資料庫 (排除 WordPress 檔案)','WordPress Files (Exclude Database)'=>'僅 WordPress 檔案 (排除資料庫)','Database + Files (WordPress Files)'=>'資料庫及 WordPress 檔案','Being subjected to mechanisms of PHP, a scheduled backup task for your site will be triggered only when the site receives at least a visit at any page.'=>'由於 PHP 機制的影響，這個網站必須在任一頁面有至少一次使用者造訪時，才會觸發這個網站的排程備份。','+ Add another schedule'=>'+ 新增其他排程','Advanced Schedule'=>'進階排程','Pro feature: learn more'=>'Pro 版功能: 進一步了解','Enable Incremental Backup'=>'啟用增量備份','Enable backup schedule'=>'啟用排程備份','Schedule Settings'=>'排程設定','Ultimate'=>'Ultimate','Freelancer'=>'Freelancer','5. Set up remote storage for child sites in bulk (for WPvivid Backup Pro only)'=>'5. 為子網站批次設定遠端儲存空間 (僅 WPvivid Backup Pro 提供)。','4. Install, claim and update WPvivid Backup Pro for child sites in bulk'=>'4. 為子網站批次安裝、通知及更新 WPvivid Backup Pro。','3. Set WPvivid Backup Free and Pro settings for all child sites'=>'3. 為全部子網站設定 WPvivid Backup 免費版及 Pro 版。','2. Set backup schedules for all child sites'=>'2. 為全部子網站設定備份排程。','1. Create and download backups for a specific child site'=>'1. 為指定子網站建立並下載備份檔案。','Download WPvivid Backup for MainWP'=>'下載 WPvivid Backup for MainWP','If you are a MainWP user, you can set up and control WPvivid Backup Free and Pro for every child site directly from your MainWP dashboard, using our WPvivid Backup for MainWP extension.'=>'MainWP 使用者使用 WPvivid Backup for MainWP 擴充功能後，便可以在 MainWP 控制台為每一個子網站設定並控制 WPvivid Backup 免費版及 Pro 版。',' Next page > '=>' 下一頁 > ',' < Pre page '=>' < 上一頁 ','Action'=>'可用操作','Log File Name'=>'記錄檔檔案名稱','Log Type'=>'記錄類型','Date'=>'日期','Website Info Value'=>'網站資訊值','Website Info Key'=>'網站資訊索引碼','Download'=>'下載','If you didn’t configure SMTP on your site, click the button below to download the relevant information (website info and error logs) to your PC when you are encountering some errors. Sending the files to us will help us diagnose what happened.'=>'如果這個網站並未完成 SMTP 組態，這個外掛發生錯誤時，請點擊下方按鈕以下載相關資訊 (網站資訊及錯誤記錄) 至裝置儲存，並將檔案傳送給我們，這能協助我們判斷問題癥結。','Method 2.'=>'方法 2','Send Debug Information to Us'=>'傳送偵錯資訊給我們','Please describe your problem here.'=>'請在這裡撰寫問題說明。','My web hosting provider is:'=>'網站使用的主機服務提供商:','I am using:'=>'網站使用的主機類型:','Your email:'=>'使用者電子郵件地址:','WPvivid support email:'=>'WPvivid 技術支援電子郵件地址:','If you have configured SMTP on your site, enter your email address and click the button below to send us the relevant information (website info and errors logs) when you are encountering errors. This will help us figure out what happened. Once the issue is resolved, we will inform you by your email address.'=>'如果網站管理員已為這個網站完成 SMTP 組態，這個外掛發生錯誤時，請輸入網站管理員的電子郵件地址，並點擊下方按鈕便能傳送相關資訊 (網站資訊及錯誤記錄) 給我們，這能協助我們判斷問題癥結。我們將問題解決後，會以相同的電子郵件地址通知你。','Method 1.'=>'方法 1','There are two ways available to send us the debug information. The first one is recommended.'=>'這裡提供 2 種能將偵錯資訊傳送給我們的方法。建議使用第 1 種方法。','Save Changes'=>'儲存設定','Premium'=>'Premium 版本','MainWP'=>'MainWP','Log'=>'記錄','Logs'=>'記錄','Debug'=>'偵錯','Remote Storage'=>'遠端儲存空間','Schedule'=>'排程','Class PclZip is not detected. Please update or reinstall your WordPress.'=>'系統沒有偵測到 PclZip 類別。請更新或重新安裝 WordPress。','Restore completed successfully.'=>'還原程序已成功完成。','Cheers! WPvivid Backup plugin has restored successfully your website. If you found WPvivid Backup plugin helpful, a 5-star rating would be highly appreciated, which motivates us to keep providing new features.'=>'大功告成！WPvivid Backup 外掛已成功還原這個網站。如果 WPvivid Backup 外掛對這個網站有所幫助，我們會很感謝使用者撰寫的 5 星評等，這能鼓勵我們持續提供新功能。','Migration is complete and htaccess file is replaced. In order to successfully complete the migration, you\'d better reinstall 301 redirect plugin, firewall and security plugin, and caching plugin if they exist.'=>'移轉已完成，且 .htaccess 檔案已完成置換。為了成功完成移轉，如果這個網站上使用 301 重新導向、防火牆/安全性及快取等外掛，建議重新安裝這些外掛。','Calculating the size of files, folder and database timed out. If you continue to receive this error, please go to the plugin settings, uncheck \'Calculate the size of files, folder and database before backing up\', save changes, then try again.'=>'計算檔案、資料夾及資料庫大小逾時。如果持續收到這個錯誤訊息，請前往外掛設定，停用 [備份前計算檔案、資料夾及資料庫大小]，然後儲存設定並再試一次。','Warning: The alias already exists in storage list.'=>'警告: 別名在儲存空間清單中已存在。','Warning: An alias for remote storage is required.'=>'警告: 遠端儲存空間需要設定別名。','Error:'=>'錯誤: ','Warning:'=>'警告:','Migrate WordPress'=>'移轉 WordPress','Restore Your Site from a Backup'=>'從備份檔案還原網站','Create a Manual Backup'=>'建立手動備份','WPvivid Backup Settings'=>'WPvivid 備份設定','How-to'=>'使用方式','Troubleshooting'=>'疑難排解','ChangeLog'=>'變更記錄','Current Version: '=>'目前版本: ','Settings'=>'設定','Backup & Restore'=>'備份及還原','https://wpvivid.com'=>'https://wpvivid.com','Clone or copy WP sites then move or migrate them to new host (new domain), schedule backups, transfer backups to leading remote storage. All in one.'=>'再製或複製 WordPress 網站，並將網站移動或移轉至新主機或新的網域名稱，還能排程備份、傳輸備份檔案至業界領先的遠端儲存空間，多種功能整合為一。','WPvivid Backup Plugin'=>'WPvivid Backup Plugin','Enter Your SFTP Account'=>'輸入 SFTP 帳戶','Enter Your Amazon S3 Account'=>'輸入 Amazon S3 帳戶','You have authenticated the Microsoft OneDrive account as your remote storage.'=>'這個網站已完成 Microsoft OneDrive 帳戶作為遠端儲存空間的驗證。','You have authenticated the Google Drive account as your remote storage.'=>'這個網站已完成 Google 雲端硬碟帳戶作為遠端儲存空間的驗證。','Enter Your DigitalOcean Spaces Account'=>'輸入 DigitalOcean Spaces 帳戶','Enter Your FTP Account'=>'輸入 FTP 帳戶','You have authenticated the Dropbox account as your remote storage.'=>'這個網站已完成 Dropbox 帳戶作為遠端儲存空間的驗證。','As Amazon S3 and DigitalOcean Space have upgraded their connection methods, please delete the previous connections and re-add your Amazon S3/DigitalOcean Space accounts to make sure the connections work.'=>'Amazon S3 及 DigitalOcean Spaces 已升級其連線方法，請刪除之前的連線，並重新新增 Amazon S3/DigitalOcean Spaces 帳戶，以確保能正常連線。','With this option checked, Pages/posts already existing will be overwritten with the updated ones in an import.'=>'勾選此選項後，較新的頁面/文章將覆蓋現有頁面/文章。','Retrieving the backup information failed while showing log. Please try again later.'=>'顯示記錄時索引備份資訊失敗，請稍後重試。','Highlighted icon illuminates that you have choosed a remote storage to store backups'=>'強調顯示的圖示會標示出已選取、用於儲存備份檔案的遠端儲存空間']];